The evidence with the title 'Trump is peddling fantasy 'facts' about immigration ' says Sep 11, 2016  ... In his speech on august 31 , Donald Trump stated that “ immigration as a share of national population is set to break all historical records ”  ... The Census Bureau 's records on the foreign - born population only go back to 1850 , but the annual rate of increase in recent years is also well within historical norms.
